# No middleware in a static export, so redirect locale-less paths to the default
# locale at the Cloudflare edge. Each locale's pages are served directly (/en, /id).
# The bare section paths keep external links locale-agnostic — e.g. the host nav
# links to `<blog>/cv`, which lands on /en/cv (see ../../docs/deployment.md).
/          /en          302
/cv        /en/cv       302
/posts     /en/posts    302
